Hence making San Marino the oldest ongoing Republic in the world and possibly making history too. Older than those of the other 2 Republics i.e. USA (1913) & Mali (1959) by the way.

One of the busiest events in San Marino in recent times was the Red Males festival also in 1955, I wrote an article about it for VietTravel Magazine
http://www.viettravelmagazine…go-your-way-id-can-thue-dac-la-6627.htm

Hope to have a chance to come back to San Marino and as many of your readers, I am an interpreter by profession. If I can help other visitors to San Marino, you can use my phone number +39 0522 290237 or my email: hetvanluong@gmail.com

Cheers,
